Busch Gardens and Sea World have announced the return of their annual Halloween event Howl-O-Scream for 2022. And in honor of today being Friday the 13th, they are holding a 24-hour flash sale. Guests can purchase two Howl-O-Scream tickets for either theme park for $66.66 through 11:59 p.m. tonight. Tickets must be purchased in pairs with a maximum of 10 tickets at the discount price. Howl-O-Scream runs Sept. 9-Oct. 31 this year, and these tickets are valid on any day of the event. To purchase tickets, go to seaworldorlando.com or howloscream.com.